jobContext:
The Admin and Procurement Officer will manage and execute administrative and procurement activities associated with the project. Reporting directly to the Coordinator (Finance) and Chief Coordinator, He/she will have to:
Serve as key point of administrative contact and liaison with internal and external stakeholders,
Provide direct support to the project staff,
Conduct and administer the day-to-day activities of the project;
Facilitates logistics, resource management, procurement and administration procedures and documentation,
Maintain inventory of goods procured under the project;
Assist in database management;
Manage procurement related formalities as per the PPR, PPA and ADB's guideline
Perform miscellaneous job-related duties as assigned by the supervisor. She/he will also work on HR and administrative related tasks/ issues.

